wikipedia_page.main: Joseph William Kinchin (11 June 1884 – 23 December 1969) was a British middle-distance runner. He competed in the men's 3200 metres steeplechase at the 1908 Summer Olympics.

response: In the first round of the 3200 metre steeplechase competition, Holdaway defeated countryman Joseph Kinchin and a pair of Americans, winning a chance to compete in the final.  There, he started off quickly but fell to fourth place, finishing with a time of 11:26.0.
